      "instruction": "<p>Gradually whisk 250ml <span class=\"text-danger\">[500ml]</span> <strong>milk</strong> into the roux, a little at a time and cook for 2-3 min or until a smooth, thick sauce remains</p><p>Remove from the heat, season with <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper </strong>– this is your<strong> béchamel sauce</strong></p><p>While the béchamel is cooking, combine the <strong>balsamic vinegar </strong>with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> – this is your<strong> dressing</strong></p><p>Wash the <strong>rocket</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen paper</p>",
